	<article class="post-619884 post type-post status-publish hentry category-dealbook-column category-healthcare category-legal category-mergers-acquisitions tag-abbott-laboratories tag-abbvie-inc tag-bresch-heather tag-corporate-taxes tag-drugs-pharmaceuticals tag-mylan-inc tag-shire-plc per-bresch-heather des-corporate-taxes des-drugs-pharmaceuticals org-abbott-laboratories org-abbvie-inc org-mylan-inc org-shire-plc news_keywords-corporate-tax news_keywords-heather-bresch news_keywords-pharmaceuticals-2" id="post-619884">
	<header class="postHeader">
