			<span class="kicker"><a href="https://dealbook.nytimes.com/category/main-topics/legal/">Legal/Regulatory</a> | <a href="https://dealbook.nytimes.com/category/columnists/dealbook-column/">DealBook Column</a></span>		</div>
				<h1 itemprop="headline" class="entry-title">Reluctantly, Patriot Flees Homeland for Greener Tax Pastures</h1>
		<div class="story-meta-footer">
			<address class="byline author vcard" itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
				By Andrew Ross Sorkin			</address>
			<!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2014-07-15T01:20:44+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">July 14, 2014 9:20 pm</time>
			<!-- date updated --><span class="visually-hidden updated">July 14, 2014 9:20 pm</span><button class="button comments-button  theme-kicker" data-skip-to-para-id="">
</button>
		</div>
			</header>
		<div class="entry-content">
	<div class="w592"><figure class="promo media video blog-video "
    data-videoid="100000002999938" data-media-action="modal" data-autoplay="" data-embedded="true" aria-label="media" role="group">
